    Scope and Contents
Soma discusses 20th century Springfield, Illinois: growing up, childhood games, chores, and diseases; schools; neighborhoods and streets; entertainment, businesses, and churches. She also discusses Petersburg, the Bates Experimental Road, WWI, and radio programs. 5 tapes, 450 mins.
Interview by Dee Nelson, 1988-89 
